title: Teams /help skills/agents list renders on one line instead of bulleted list
---
The /help command in Teams produces a table (formats correctly) followed by a list of skills and agents. The list portion renders on a single line instead of as separate items.

Expected: bullet list or line-separated items
Actual: all skills/agents on one line

Likely cause: Teams markdown rendering differs from Telegram; may need explicit bullet syntax (`- item`) or newline handling. Check slash_commands_fmt.ml format_help and how Teams adapter renders multi-line text vs markdown.